data.description: Just Reduced! Nestled in a neighborhood that proudly boasts no city taxes, this home provides a serene and picturesque environment. Discover the epitome of comfortable and peaceful living in this exceptional split-level home. Enjoy the perks of living in an area with all the amenities and conveniences you need! Don't miss your chance to experience the joys of its breathtaking garden that has been carefully maintained! The interior of this split-level gem is equally impressive. The main level welcomes you with an abundance of natural light flowing through the windows, illuminating the inviting living and dining areas. The modern kitchen, adorned with granite countertops and stainless steel appliances, is a culinary enthusiast's dream. Downstairs, the family room basement offers a cozy retreat with a fireplace, making it an excellent space for movie nights, game days, or simply relaxing with loved ones. There's also a convenient half bathroom on this level. The roof and HVAC are only 6 years old.  This split-level home is a rare find!
